====================
Description:
====================
Plot AvsE distributions from the 208Tl 2614 keV DEP region of calibration runs. Focus on the good HG channels in the following DS4 calibration run ranges.
60001442 60001461
60001508 60001521 <--- last "good" cal of DS4
60001578 60001592
60001720 60001732
60001855 60001868
60001914 60001926

Excluded HG channels are: 1108,1110,1138,1140,1142,1144,1168,1202,1206,1208,1234,1238,1268,1302,1304,1328

Note that some directories, plotting parameters, etc were hardcoded for expediency.
====================
Instructions:
====================
1.) Make an up-to-date DSChannelMaps.root file by executing the CreateDSChannelMapsFile.C ROOT macro.
2.) Run CalibrationAvsE.cc on each needed calibration run range. The associated DS also needs to be specified. This produces root files of AvsE histograms for each channel and energy region.
3.) Run SavePlots_CalibrationAvsE.cc on each needed calibration run range -- with DS also specified. This produces PDF files for each channel with the various AvsE distributions for a channel plotted on the same plot.
4.) Optional: can run PlotChan_CalibrationAvsE.cc to make the overlayed plot for a single channel in a single calibration run range.
